name: FREAKOLOCO! 62 2/2
description: These Siamese brothers were good friends, until the invention of cryptocurrencies and NFT. This green guy, Carlos, is a great artist and has learned a lot about 3D modeling and animations with state-of-the-art special effects. He is very funny, but sometimes he doesn't stop talking and this can be annoying. One of his hobbies is making custom action figures and playing The Legend of Selda: Marajoaras Mask. These brothers started fighting after we had taken a picture of them to sell them as NFT. Carlos wanted to sell on the Hic et Nunc (HEN) platform and his brother on OPENSEA . They started spitting at each other and trying to poke each other in the eye. We had to break up the fight and decided to sell half the image on each platform. The funny thing is that they have the same girlfriend and poop through the same hole. Type: Creature / Edition: 3rd / Alignment: True Neutral / Height: 177.5 Cm / Weight: 87.5 Kg / Strenght: 50 / Dexterity: 15 / Constitution: 30 / Intelligence: 50 / Wisdom: 15 / Charisma: 80.
